creator: Roy Rockwood
description:
LibriVox recording of Dave Dashaway Around the World by Roy Rockwood.
Read in English by Scott Danneker
Never was there a more clever young aviator than Dave Dashaway, and all up-to-date lads will wish to make his acquaintance. In this absorbing tale Dave and his chums attempt a great air flight around the world. Filled with hairbreadth adventures in Alaska, Siberia and elsewhere, Dave Dashaway Around the World presents a true-to-life picture of what may be accomplished in the near future. (From Cupples & Leon Co., Publishers, New York)
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
